text: Yun Daek (born 22 September 1940) is a South Korean wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle featherweight at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of South Korea Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
